== Media coverage ==

Scottish Cup matches are currently broadcast live by both [[BBC Scotland]] and [[Sky Sports]]<ref name="bbc-rights">[http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/scotland/7544606.stm BBC Sport | Scotland | TV rights boost for Scottish FA]</ref>.

